QuestData.Title: Survival Ring: Blades
QuestData.Description: This is one of the challenges I put upon my warriors to keep them strong and fast. Let's see how you fare.$B$BSurvive the ring for 60 seconds without getting pushed out or killed. Stay on your toes.
QuestData.LogDescription: Enter the Survival Ring and survive for 60 seconds without leaving.

Objectives.Objective: Live through the Survival Ring for 60 seconds
